    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pork</strong> <strong>meatballs</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) (use <strong>baking paper</strong> to avoid mess!) and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-18 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1688738004345-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1688738004345-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1688738004345-x700.jpg",
