            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Spanish-style pork meatballs with tomato & cannellini bean stew </strong>in a bowl and the <strong>buttered</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> to the side</p><p>Taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>if needed</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped parsley</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the parsley!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
